features: High-Quality Poly Project Organizer: KTRIO project organizer is made of sturdy polypropylene material, ensuring exceptional durability and longevity. It is tear-proof, water-resistant, archival safe, and completely free of PVC. This multi-pocket folder can prevent the folder from wrinkling and stay open, providing a sturdy and reliable solution for your organizational needs.

Large Capacity School Organization Tool: Our poly project organizer features 12 pockets and 6 dividers with 1/6-cut assorted tabs in bright colors. It also includes a pocket on the front cover and an additional zip pouch on the back cover. The folders with pockets are designed to hold standard letter size 8.5 x 11 inch paper, with each pocket capable of storing up to 30-40 pages. This offers exceptional value for all users.

Customizable Front Cover & Secure Stay Put Tabs & Extra Storage with Back Zipper Pouch: The transparent pocket on the front cover allows for complete customization of your folder for your school schedule or personal preference. The special stay put tabs inside the folder keep your papers securely in place, preventing them from sliding out. Additionally, the clear poly zip pouch on the inside back cover provides extra storage for writing utensils, notecards, stickers, and more.

Write and Reusable Erase Color Round Tabs: Our project folder includes reusable colored round tabs, allowing for quick writing and easy erasing. The thoughtful design enables efficient location and categorization with the assorted color tabs. Furthermore, we provide an additional 24 replaceable white index labels for added convenience.

Versatile Use & Excellent Customer Service: This 12 pocket folder organizer is ideal for categorizing and organizing homework, home or office paperwork, bills, and other paper documents. It is suitable for use at home, in the office, or in the classroom. KTRIO is a trusted professional office supply manufacturer. If you have any quality issues, please don't hesitate to contact us. We assure you of a prompt response within 12 hours.

reviews.reviewText: I purchased specifically for organizing my ESY program. This had the perfect number of sections and is very durable for throwing in my bag. I was able to organize time sheets, attendance, class lists, busing, etc. Everything was easy to find and/or file as needed.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for organizing worksheets
reviews.reviewText: I originally ordered this for organizing manuals. It didn’t work for that purpose as well as I had hoped. However, I also have a preschooler and we attend a co-op. This folder has been perfect for organizing and separating worksheets for his class. The plastic is sturdy enough to prevent the papers from getting crunched in the book bag. The tabs are handy. The clear pocket in the front did pull away from the cover, but so far hot glue had held it in place. Over all, for the right application, this is a good product.
